data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, ranch home situated in a quaint neighborhood! The central location is perfect proximity to the desirable Nixa schools and shopping!! The large, fenced-in backyard provides an intimate setting with mature trees and plenty of space for outdoor activities!! Super- cozy woodburning fireplace offers a warm welcome in the living room. Updated backsplash in the kitchen, new roof, new high-capacity water heater, Wifi controlled garage and thermostat, and all the stainless-steel appliances included are just a few bonus features that make this gem affordable priced!! Clean and move-in ready!!
